  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to explore whether the addition of Hemopatch to standard care
      can reduce prolonged air leaks and shorten the use of air drainage tube after surgery in
      thoracic lung surgery patients at high risk for prolonged air leaks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
